00:01:50.520 --> 00:01:51.440
What address?

00:01:51.440 --> 00:01:52.600
There was no address.

00:01:52.600 --> 00:01:53.760
She didn't give us anything.

00:01:53.760 --> 00:01:55.426
I was in the hospital
after a miscarriage,

00:01:55.448 --> 00:01:56.800
and you had just had twins.

00:01:56.800 --> 00:01:57.080
Yes.

00:01:57.093 --> 00:01:58.360
Your family was struggling,

00:01:58.440 --> 00:01:59.559
so you kept the boy

00:01:59.559 --> 00:02:00.600
and gave away the girl.

00:02:00.600 --> 00:02:01.130
That's not...

00:02:01.137 --> 00:02:02.390
You said we could take her.

00:02:02.399 --> 00:02:03.080
And you said,

00:02:03.080 --> 00:02:05.919
"Raise her as your own.
Let's never contact each other again."

00:02:05.919 --> 00:02:07.160
No, that's not true!

00:02:07.160 --> 00:02:09.360
It's not! My mother wouldn't do that.

00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:10.999
You can't say that.

00:02:10.999 --> 00:02:12.679
That's not what my mother told me.

00:02:12.679 --> 00:02:13.960
Not what your mother told you?

00:02:13.960 --> 00:02:15.782
Your mother did many
things behind your back.

00:02:15.782 --> 00:02:17.871
She gave your daughter
away without your knowledge,

00:02:17.871 --> 00:02:18.360
didn't she?

00:02:18.404 --> 00:02:20.360
Please stop.

00:02:20.360 --> 00:02:21.360
Please just stop.

00:02:21.800 --> 00:02:23.800
I'm sorry. This is our fault.

00:02:23.960 --> 00:02:25.480
It's all our fault, okay?

00:02:25.520 --> 00:02:27.520
I won't say anything more.

00:02:28.480 --> 00:02:29.159
Mingzhu.

00:02:30.559 --> 00:02:32.080
Please forgive Mommy, okay?

00:02:32.320 --> 00:02:34.040
I'm sorry.

00:02:34.200 --> 00:02:34.999
What did you say?

00:02:35.960 --> 00:02:36.920
What Mommy?

00:02:37.040 --> 00:02:38.080
Whose mommy?

00:02:38.960 --> 00:02:40.520
The audacity of you.

00:02:40.520 --> 00:02:42.520
Thirty years ago,
during the hardest times,

00:02:42.520 --> 00:02:43.839
you threw your child away

00:02:43.839 --> 00:02:45.320
and never looked back.

00:02:45.320 --> 00:02:46.800
We were the ones

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:47.839
who raised her.

00:02:47.839 --> 00:02:48.399
You're right.

00:02:48.399 --> 00:02:49.399
