00:03:10.839 --> 00:03:12.520
Please listen to me.

00:03:13.320 --> 00:03:14.439
I didn't personally

00:03:14.839 --> 00:03:17.520
give her to you,

00:03:18.399 --> 00:03:21.080
and you know that.

00:03:21.360 --> 00:03:23.800
