00:06:18.039 --> 00:06:19.560
Let's die together!

00:06:19.560 --> 00:06:20.640
- Yu Jingxiang!
- Let's die!

00:06:20.640 --> 00:06:21.599
Yu Jingxiang!

00:06:21.599 --> 00:06:22.799
- Let's die!
- Listen!

