00:07:37.839 --> 00:07:38.560
I know.

00:07:38.560 --> 00:07:39.520
And you were

00:07:39.919 --> 00:07:41.200
so busy with work

00:07:41.200 --> 00:07:43.479
because we were poor.

00:07:43.960 --> 00:07:45.520
And that's not all,

00:07:45.520 --> 00:07:46.680
you know what else she said?

00:07:47.080 --> 00:07:48.880
She said she hemorrhaged badly,

00:07:48.880 --> 00:07:50.279
and she didn't know her mom

00:07:50.279 --> 00:07:51.320
would give her child away.

00:07:51.640 --> 00:07:52.520
She didn't know!

00:07:52.520 --> 00:07:53.760
Maybe she didn't know at first,

00:07:53.770 --> 00:07:55.830
but for 30 years? All these years,
and she never knew?

00:07:55.839 --> 00:07:56.479
Yes.

00:07:56.599 --> 00:07:58.760
Their family does seem unreliable.

00:07:58.919 --> 00:08:00.399
Especially Xu Dacheng.

00:08:00.399 --> 00:08:02.560
He's downright shady and
his methods are underhanded.

00:08:03.080 --> 00:08:04.919
