she realized she went too far
after she got home.

00:30:00.680 --> 00:30:03.920
So, she thought she should give you
some supplements for your health.

00:30:06.479 --> 00:30:07.039
Okay.

00:30:09.279 --> 00:30:09.960
Mingzhu,

00:30:10.360 --> 00:30:11.519
