00:30:11.840 --> 00:30:13.440
Are you hungry?

00:30:13.519 --> 00:30:14.440
I'll make you some tea.

00:30:14.460 --> 00:30:16.120
- Why are you sitting there?
- Make her something to drink.

00:30:16.120 --> 00:30:18.160
Go make some tea.

00:30:18.160 --> 00:30:19.559
I'll get you something to drink.

00:30:19.559 --> 00:30:20.600
Please wait here.

00:30:20.600 --> 00:30:22.204
I'm going to get you some food.

00:30:22.204 --> 00:30:22.750
Wait here.

00:30:22.999 --> 00:30:24.400
Don't eat it on your own.

00:30:24.400 --> 00:30:24.920
Here.

00:30:25.239 --> 00:30:26.799
Mingzhu, try this.

00:30:27.319 --> 00:30:28.559
Let's see.

00:30:29.680 --> 00:30:30.680
Jealous?

00:30:31.360 --> 00:30:32.239
Feeling unfair?

00:30:32.960 --> 00:30:33.880
I'm used to it.

00:30:34.039 --> 00:30:34.719
Mingzhu,

00:30:35.048 --> 00:30:36.110
this happens all the time.

00:30:36.680 --> 00:30:37.559
Move.

00:30:37.799 --> 00:30:38.400
Legs up.

00:30:39.880 --> 00:30:40.559
Here.

00:30:40.559 --> 00:30:41.920
Try these dates.

00:30:43.479 --> 00:30:44.200
What is this?

00:30:44.200 --> 00:30:45.039
You can't eat this.

00:30:45.039 --> 00:30:46.440
Move, move.

00:30:46.600 --> 00:30:48.120
Mingzhu,

00:30:48.239 --> 00:30:50.039
our fruits aren't fresh enough.

00:30:50.160 --> 00:30:52.279
I'll just peel you a cucumber.

00:30:52.799 --> 00:30:53.360
This won't do.

00:30:54.799 --> 00:30:56.079
Go buy some fruits.

00:30:56.079 --> 00:30:57.050
The most expensive ones.

00:30:57.160 --> 00:30:58.600
It's really fine. You don't have to.

00:30:58.840 --> 00:30:59.559
Mingzhu,

00:30:59.920 --> 00:31:00.920
just leave them be.

00:31:01.079 --> 00:31:01.880
See? I told you.

00:31:01.960 --> 00:31:03.004
You're the miracle cure.

00:31:03.048 --> 00:31:04.120
You fixed them right up.

00:31:04.239 --> 00:31:05.559
You instantly turned two old folks

00:31:06.279 --> 00:31:08.120
ready to tear each other's hair out

00:31:08.840 --> 00:31:10.559
into a picture of marital bliss.

00:31:11.360 --> 00:31:12.559
Xu Zhidong and I

00:31:12.559 --> 00:31:13.719
are no match for you.

00:31:16.039 --> 00:31:17.239
Let's open this up.

00:31:17.239 --> 00:31:17.640
Okay.

00:31:17.640 --> 00:31:18.880
Here, try it.

00:31:18.880 --> 00:31:20.239
Yes, this one.

00:31:20.640 --> 00:31:21.680
She must be hungry.

00:31:21.960 --> 00:31:23.920
Let her try it one by one.

00:31:23.920 --> 00:31:24.400
Look at you.

00:31:24.400 --> 00:31:25.799
Here, open up.

00:31:27.871 --> 00:31:28.880
You don't like sweet food?

00:31:28.880 --> 00:31:29.440
Mom,

00:31:30.319 --> 00:31:31.120
I'm hungry too.

00:31:31.479 --> 00:31:32.960
There are steamed buns in the fridge.

00:31:32.960 --> 00:31:33.880
Go get them yourself.

00:31:34.048 --> 00:31:35.840
You want to drink this?
I'll open it for you.

00:31:35.840 --> 00:31:36.719
But is cold drink okay?

00:31:36.719 --> 00:31:38.200
It's okay. I got this.

00:31:38.279 --> 00:31:39.039
It's cold.

00:31:43.079 --> 00:31:44.120
Honestly,

00:31:44.160 --> 00:31:45.239
our banquet hall

00:31:45.239 --> 00:31:46.519
is indeed a bit dated.

00:31:47.079 --> 00:31:48.719
I've asked management before

00:31:48.719 --> 00:31:49.840
about renovating it,

00:31:50.440 --> 00:31:51.799
but they didn't agree.

00:31:52.319 --> 00:31:53.519
Why didn't they agree?

00:31:54.759 --> 00:31:55.440
No budget.

00:31:56.039 --> 00:31:57.319
Just like us.

00:31:58.640 --> 00:32:00.920
I have a good friend
who works in wedding planning.

00:32:00.920 --> 00:32:01.880
She's amazing.

00:32:01.960 --> 00:32:04.826
She can turn old into vintage,
designing all kinds of retro themes.

00:32:05.440 --> 00:32:06.960
Here, take a look at these mock-ups.

00:32:09.448 --> 00:32:10.550
This one's Hong Kongâ€“style,

00:32:11.920 --> 00:32:12.920
this one's Republic-era,

00:32:13.920 --> 00:32:15.600
and this one's 1980s retro.

00:32:16.239 --> 00:32:17.479
See which one you like.

00:32:18.600 --> 00:32:19.719
They're all pretty cool.

00:32:19.719 --> 00:32:20.319
Yes.

00:32:20.560 --> 00:32:21.710
Which one do you like best?

00:32:22.440 --> 00:32:23.799
I think

00:32:24.319 --> 00:32:25.759
I like the Republic-era theme.

00:32:26.120 --> 00:32:27.279
It feels so elegant.

00:32:27.560 --> 00:32:29.310
Lijun Hotel doesn't have
this kind of vibe.

00:32:29.759 --> 00:32:31.160
You checked out Lijun?

00:32:31.440 --> 00:32:31.960
Yes.

00:32:32.440 --> 00:32:34.360
It was 8,888 yuan per table.

00:32:34.440 --> 00:32:35.693
That's just the starting price.

00:32:36.400 --> 00:32:37.079
Honestly,

00:32:37.400 --> 00:32:39.440
Lijun is fancier than our place.

00:32:39.782 --> 00:32:41.840
River view, grand dome ceiling,
really impressive.

00:32:42.360 --> 00:32:44.079
My sister-in-law actually works there.

00:32:44.093 --> 00:32:45.640
What's your sister-in-law's name?

00:32:45.880 --> 00:32:46.640
Feng Meiqi.

00:32:47.479 --> 00:32:48.319
Really?

00:32:48.920 --> 00:32:50.440
What a small world!

00:32:51.079 --> 00:32:52.559
She's my closest high school friend.

00:32:52.559 --> 00:32:53.799
I'm going to video call her now.

00:32:53.826 --> 00:32:54.510
That's not necessary.

00:32:54.519 --> 00:32:55.279
It's fine.

00:32:56.400 --> 00:32:57.079
Meiqi,

00:32:57.440 --> 00:32:58.479
look who this is.

00:32:59.479 --> 00:33:00.239
Hi, Meiqi.

00:33:01.600 --> 00:33:02.479
Mingzhu?

00:33:02.719 --> 00:33:03.920
What are you doing together?

00:33:05.479 --> 00:33:06.920
I'm introducing them

00:33:06.920 --> 00:33:08.279
our hotel's wedding hall.

00:33:08.719 --> 00:33:10.479
Sorry for snatching your client.

00:33:11.239 --> 00:33:11.960
It's fine.

00:33:12.920 --> 00:33:14.279
Nanxi Hotel is more economical.

00:33:15.479 --> 00:33:18.239
Yes, because we can't afford Lijun.

00:33:19.519 --> 00:33:20.200
By the way,

00:33:20.200 --> 00:33:21.440
did you know that Mingzhu

00:33:21.440 --> 00:33:23.160
is my boyfriend's long-lost sister?

00:33:25.440 --> 00:33:25.960
Really?

00:33:27.039 --> 00:33:28.920
Mingzhu, you found your birth parents?

00:33:31.319 --> 00:33:32.719
It just happened recently.

00:33:33.079 --> 00:33:34.640
Why didn't you tell us?

00:33:35.880 --> 00:33:36.960
I haven't had the chance.

00:33:38.960 --> 00:33:39.640
Meiqi,

00:33:39.799 --> 00:33:41.360
let me show you the other venue options.

00:33:43.479 --> 00:33:44.960
Did we cause you trouble?

00:33:45.640 --> 00:33:46.200
No. It's fine.

00:33:46.840 --> 00:33:47.479
Oh, no.

00:33:48.479 --> 00:33:49.960
Oh, no, this is bad.

00:33:50.920 --> 00:33:52.279
Really bad.

00:33:53.239 --> 00:33:55.960
Shen Mingzhu suddenly
has two new parents,

00:33:56.279 --> 00:33:58.680
an older sister, and a little brother.

00:33:59.160 --> 00:34:00.759
And they are just ordinary folks,

00:34:00.759 --> 00:34:02.239
no money, no status, no resources.

00:34:02.239 --> 00:34:03.479
They can't help with anything.

00:34:07.799 --> 00:34:09.199
What if one day they expect us

00:34:09.199 --> 00:34:11.240
to use our connections for them?

00:34:11.960 --> 00:34:13.280
Come on, it's not that serious.

00:34:14.320 --> 00:34:14.920
Don't

00:34:14.999 --> 00:34:17.079
work yourself up over things

00:34:17.079 --> 00:34:18.119
that haven't even happened.

00:34:18.159 --> 00:34:20.159
Dad's right.

00:34:21.119 --> 00:34:22.840
I simply shared that to you as a gossip.

00:34:22.840 --> 00:34:24.079
And you're overreacting.

00:34:24.240 --> 00:34:25.679
I won't tell you anything next time.

00:34:25.720 --> 00:34:26.479
Feng Meiqi,

00:34:27.079 --> 00:34:28.800
you're too young and naive.

00:34:28.800 --> 00:34:29.760
You don't understand.

00:34:29.871 --> 00:34:31.150
And you, why are you laughing?

00:34:31.159 --> 00:34:31.880
You're no better,

00:34:31.880 --> 00:34:33.159
never care about anything!

00:34:33.479 --> 00:34:34.479
I'm telling you both,

00:34:35.240 --> 00:34:36.760
this is serious.

00:34:38.360 --> 00:34:40.639
Shen Mingzhu didn't
even tell us about this.

00:34:41.400 --> 00:34:43.559
Do you know what that means?

00:34:43.559 --> 00:34:44.760
What does it mean?

00:34:46.400 --> 00:34:48.240
It means Shen Mingzhu's loyalty

00:34:48.920 --> 00:34:50.240
is wavering.

00:34:50.960 --> 00:34:51.960
It means

00:34:51.960 --> 00:34:54.960
she doesn't see us as her own family.

