00:39:14.599 --> 00:39:15.760
It's from my mother-in-law.

00:39:16.519 --> 00:39:18.199
You should wear it all the time.

00:39:18.199 --> 00:39:19.920
No way. It's a family heirloom.

00:39:24.920 --> 00:39:27.280
You know, my husband looks so handsome.

00:39:27.840 --> 00:39:28.999
Alright, everything's ready.

00:39:28.999 --> 00:39:29.599
Let's go.

00:39:29.760 --> 00:39:30.920
Zhidong!

00:39:32.479 --> 00:39:33.400
Zhidong!

00:39:34.079 --> 00:39:35.720
- Coming!
- It's time to go!

00:39:35.960 --> 00:39:37.479
Mom, you forgot the ginseng!

00:39:37.720 --> 00:39:39.479
You're the one who should carry it!

00:39:39.960 --> 00:39:42.400
We're going to Bichen's house!
Why are you dawdling?

00:39:42.400 --> 00:39:42.960
Mom,

00:39:43.720 --> 00:39:44.960
is the bride price all ready?

00:39:46.720 --> 00:39:47.639
The bride price

00:39:48.240 --> 00:39:49.679
is all in the bank.

00:39:50.240 --> 00:39:52.004
I thought we were giving it
to them today?

00:39:54.320 --> 00:39:55.039
Zhidong,

00:39:55.400 --> 00:39:56.240
here's the thing,

00:39:58.479 --> 00:40:00.199
I'll explain it clearly

00:40:00.199 --> 00:40:01.400
to Bichen's parents.

00:40:02.479 --> 00:40:03.920
We'll give the bride price

00:40:04.880 --> 00:40:06.800
to the bride

00:40:06.800 --> 00:40:08.079
on the wedding eve party.

00:40:08.840 --> 00:40:09.920
You just tell them

00:40:10.079 --> 00:40:12.360
it's an old tradition from our hometown.

00:40:12.360 --> 00:40:13.280
An old custom.

00:40:13.840 --> 00:40:14.440
Dad,

00:40:15.199 --> 00:40:16.440
what wedding eve party?

00:40:16.440 --> 00:40:17.493
Do we have such a custom?

00:40:18.159 --> 00:40:18.920
Your mom

00:40:18.920 --> 00:40:20.079
is clearly joking.

00:40:20.479 --> 00:40:21.240
Fine, fine.

00:40:21.639 --> 00:40:22.479
Xu Dacheng,

00:40:23.880 --> 00:40:25.880
200,000 is not a small amount.

00:40:25.880 --> 00:40:27.119
I know, I know.

00:40:27.479 --> 00:40:28.079
Zhidong,

00:40:28.479 --> 00:40:30.599
mine and your father's life savings

00:40:30.599 --> 00:40:31.669
are in there,

00:40:31.670 --> 00:40:33.337
plus your sister's 100,000!

00:40:33.360 --> 00:40:34.440
And I'm eternally grateful.

00:40:34.440 --> 00:40:35.537
Besides, just in case...

00:40:35.760 --> 00:40:36.720
I'm just saying in case,

00:40:37.360 --> 00:40:39.400
