with you and Bichen...

00:40:39.400 --> 00:40:40.280
That's impossible.

00:40:40.280 --> 00:40:41.720
I know it's impossible!

00:40:41.720 --> 00:40:43.240
I'm just talking about a "what if",

00:40:43.679 --> 00:40:44.320
right?

00:40:45.915 --> 00:40:48.550
It's much harder to get money
back than it is to give it away.

00:40:49.079 --> 00:40:50.159
Alright, don't worry.

00:40:50.479 --> 00:40:51.840
Your mother knows what she's doing.

00:40:51.960 --> 00:40:52.599
Okay.

00:40:52.648 --> 00:40:53.630
Just wish me the best.

00:40:53.880 --> 00:40:54.629
Alright!

00:40:54.630 --> 00:40:55.537
Off to buy groceries?

00:40:56.720 --> 00:40:58.240
You're all dressed so formally.

00:40:58.240 --> 00:40:59.440
Where are you going?

00:41:00.599 --> 00:41:01.920
Paying a visit to the in-laws!

00:41:02.599 --> 00:41:03.320
Zhidong,

00:41:03.760 --> 00:41:05.320
when's the wedding banquet?

00:41:05.337 --> 00:41:07.440
Soon, Madam Zheng. I'll send you
an invitation when it's time.

00:41:07.440 --> 00:41:08.639
Alright, I'll be waiting!

00:41:08.639 --> 00:41:11.199
A son's wedding will
be the death of his father!

00:41:11.840 --> 00:41:12.960
But it's a happy occasion!

00:41:12.960 --> 00:41:14.320
The exhaustion is worth it!

00:41:14.960 --> 00:41:15.920
That's right.

00:41:15.960 --> 00:41:16.639
Easy there.

00:41:16.639 --> 00:41:17.479
Careful.

00:41:18.240 --> 00:41:19.119
I got in.

00:41:21.720 --> 00:41:22.240
Alright!

