I've been busy planning
a wedding banquet lately.

00:41:34.004 --> 00:41:34.960
Strangely, keeping busy

00:41:34.960 --> 00:41:36.559
has helped me eat and sleep better.

00:41:36.560 --> 00:41:38.226
Because you're
keeping yourself occupied.

00:41:38.248 --> 00:41:39.620
But still, don't overwork yourself.

00:41:40.671 --> 00:41:42.440
By the way, I wanted
to ask you something.

00:41:42.440 --> 00:41:44.280
My uncle is turning 70 next month.

00:41:44.280 --> 00:41:46.115
Does Nanxi Hotel
handle birthday banquets?

00:41:46.137 --> 00:41:47.093
Of course we do!

00:41:47.226 --> 00:41:49.320
If you book with us,
I'll get a discount for you.

00:41:49.320 --> 00:41:50.693
Great, I'll let the family know.

00:41:50.700 --> 00:41:52.880
I'll visit your hotel this weekend
to take a look first.

00:41:52.880 --> 00:41:53.960
Sure, no problem.

00:41:53.960 --> 00:41:55.400
Just call me before you come.

00:41:55.400 --> 00:41:56.199
Sure.

00:41:56.400 --> 00:41:56.920
I'm done.

00:41:56.920 --> 00:41:57.720
Take care.

00:41:57.840 --> 00:41:58.400
Bye.

